ques.p: To ask the Secretary of State for Communities and Local Government what the value of council tax receipts was in each Government office region in England in each year since 1997-98.

reply.p: Details of the council tax collected in each Government office region in England in each year since 1997-98 are shown in the following table. The figures are shown in £000 and are the amount collected within the year, irrespective of the year to which the money relates. The figures include both arrears received for previous years and prepayment of council tax for subsequent years but exclude amounts funded by council tax benefit.
